ServerBooster is a REMASTERED version of the original abandoned plugin
(2023-2024). SrCodex is NOT the original author, but is responsible for the
complete rewrite, modernization, and continued maintenance of this project.

This project was initially released as Open Source in good faith to support
the Minecraft community. After several months of free maintenance and updates,
the project has transitioned to a proprietary model to ensure its long-term
sustainability and continued development.

